Wordgen generates a list of unique words, and subtracts various words which people dislike.
This uses the wordlist from http://dreamsteep.com/projects/53-the-english-open-word-list-eowl.html

It isn't in any way optimized, or even very efficient. 
Luckily, it doesn't need to be run very often. 


